SCHEMA-AWARE FIELD PICKING (for tooltips + inspector summaries)
- Use /graph/schema hints: sortable/filterable/heavy
- Never show heavy STRUCT/arrays by default
Default key fields by edge type:
- ASSOCIATED_WITH_DISEASE: overall_score, evidence_count, num_datatypes, source
- CURATED_FOR/CAUSES/INHERITED_CAUSE_OF: classification/confidence_category, expert_panel/panel, source
- TARGETS: action_type, mechanism_of_action, num_sources, max_clinical_phase
- INDICATED_FOR: max_clinical_phase, num_sources, primary_source
- HAS_SIDE_EFFECT/HAS_ADVERSE_REACTION: frequency/report_count, llr, source
- PREDICTED_TO_AFFECT: max_l2g_score, confidence, distance_*, n_loci
- GO/ontology edges: distance, relationship_type

================================================================
ACCEPTANCE METRICS (simple)
- Time-to-understand (hover): user can explain a node’s neighborhood in < 5s
- Time-to-trust (edge click): user sees evidence summary in < 1 click
- Expansion confidence: user can undo and not feel “lost”
- Performance: expand merges without obvious stutter on typical graphs
